# Project (always read)

**STRD** — Blake Zajac portfolio/marketing site. Work in progress; follow existing patterns before introducing new architecture.

## Stack

- Astro 5 (`output: "server"`), `@astrojs/vercel`, MDX, sitemap, Sass, Zod content collections
- Site URL: `https://blakezajac.com` — sync `astro.config.mjs` `site` ↔ `src/lib/site.ts` `SITE_URL`
- Fonts: Typekit in `Layout.astro`; token `$font-family-01`
- UI import alias: `@components` → `src/components/index.ts`

## Commands

`npm run dev` · `npm run build` · `npm run preview`

## Source layout

| Path | Role |
|------|------|
| `src/components/blocks/` | `block-*.astro` — markup-only UI |
| `src/components/layouts/` | `layout-*.astro` — section shells + composition |
| `src/components/index.ts` | Re-exports blocks and layouts for `@components` |
| `src/layouts/` | `Layout.astro`, `ContentLayout.astro` (HTML document) |
| `src/pages/` | Routes + `api/` |
| `src/content/` | MDX collections + static JSON |
| `src/lib/` | Shared TS (`site`, `schema`, `actions`, SEO helpers) |
| `src/actions/` | Astro Actions (contact → Resend) |
| `src/scss/style.scss` | **Only** global CSS entry (imported in `Layout.astro`) |
| `public/` | Static assets |

**Do not edit `dist/`** as source. No Gulp — Vite/Astro compile everything.

## Rule files (detail by area)

| File | When it applies |
|------|-----------------|
| `astro.mdc` | `src/**/*.astro` |
| `scss.mdc` | `src/scss/**` |
| `typescript.mdc` | `src/lib`, `actions`, `content/config`, `pages/api` |

## New UI checklist

1. **Block or layout?** Reusable markup without section shell → `blocks/block-<name>.astro` + SCSS `components/_<name>.scss`. Full section → `layouts/layout-<name>.astro`. Export both from `index.ts` if public to pages.
2. Register SCSS in `style.scss` (`components/` for blocks; `layout/` for site chrome; `pages/` for page-specific).
3. Pages compose **layouts** from `@components`; drop **blocks** into layout slots when needed.
4. `js-*` on scripted nodes; client script in the owning `.astro` only.
5. `@use "abstracts" as *;` in SCSS; MQ4 `(width >= …)` / `(width < …)`.
6. CTAs: `primaryAction` / `secondaryAction` via `BlockButtonGroup` or `LayoutHero`; defaults in `src/lib/actions.ts`. Pass `null` to suppress on pages that already have their own CTA (contact, work index, service pillar, etc.).
7. Content: extend `content/config.ts` + MDX/JSON — **no CMS**

## Tone & deploy

- Australian English; sentence case for headings/buttons unless design says otherwise
- Contact: `/contact/?source=...` for campaign tracking; SEO landings use `?source=seo&campaign=...`
- Vercel adapter; env: `RESEND_*` for form — never commit `.env`
